headline: U.S. Bank Announces Leader for Investment Services Division
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, April 21, 2025--U.S. Bank today announced that it has united its Global Fund Services and Global Corporate Trust teams into a single Investment Services division led by Jay Martin.
